{"id":565214,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/网络民议︱《建军大业》不让评论-愤怒的豆友把评/","date":"2017-07-30T08:19:54Z","modified":"2017-07-30T08:19:54Z","title":"网络民议︱《建军大业》不让评论 愤怒的豆友把评论发《夜半凶铃》那了","content":"<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-565215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-565216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150121214450267_151722341893177_1081x558.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-565217\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125683782274_151722341893177_720x1280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-565215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565219\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150121214450267_151722341893177_1081x558-1-300x154.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150121214450267_151722341893177_1081x558-1-300x154.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150121214450267_151722341893177_1081x558-1.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565218\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280-1-169x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"1049\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280-1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280-1-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125665833489_151722341893177_720x1280-1.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565220\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125683782274_151722341893177_720x1280-1-169x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"1049\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125683782274_151722341893177_720x1280-1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125683782274_151722341893177_720x1280-1-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/BbsImg150125683782274_151722341893177_720x1280-1.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>以下为《中国数字时代》编辑摘录的部分评论：</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>有本事放开评论啊</p>\n<p>《建dang伟业》又不是没放开过，还没上映评分就在3分以下</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>可想而知豆瓣评分的公正性如何了</p>\n<p>也不一定完全是，但是有两种电影打分是绝对不客观的：文艺小清新电影和以D为主题的电影。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大禹治水都知道堵不如疏一部电影而已至于怕成这样嘛，有人无脑黑就有人客观评价现在为了屏蔽无脑黑就一刀切全屏蔽了，因噎废食</p>\n<p>治水又不是光梳不堵，治水你也得建堤坝让水乖乖的走你想让它走的河道，光梳不堵就成了黄泛区了</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>豆瓣不开评分也是对的，不然一堆屁股歪上天的键盘斗士刷一星</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>说豆瓣反体制的，威虎山、湄公河之类分数不算低吧？</p>\n<p>我记得前两个大爷曾经也是让评的，谁还有截图</p>\n<p>这俩电影就是套了主旋律的外衣拍的动作片</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>没人发现《午夜凶铃》最倒霉吗 躺着也中枪</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>前两个业当年是开放打分了吧？</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>豆瓣这是有病吧，那夜半凶铃何其无辜啊</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>人家评论《夜半凶铃》，其实是为了评论建军大业，其实延伸出去，人家真的想评论建军大业么，是不是也是在试图评论一些不让评论的东西呢？面对问题是解决问题的第一步，堵住别人的嘴只不过是掩耳盗铃罢了</p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,17016],"tags":[31512,33120,33090,33121,14804]}